snippet.title: Giving My Twin Babies up for Adoption - A Sad Brookhaven Story
snippet.description:
In this Roblox Brookhaven, A mom gives her babies up for adoption. One grows up poor and one rich. 
Later on in Brookhaven high school, they meet for the first time. What will happen when they realize they look identical? Find out what happens in this heartfelt Robox RP Story with Titi Games.
